|WKO~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DarkWind Player Levels
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
|MKBADVANCEMENT:
  |YKOAdvancing a level costs experience. Characters can advance
  manually by visiting an Adventurer's Guild, or by using
  |YKBautolevel on |YKOto spend exp and gain levels automatically.
  Remort characters always level automatically.

|MKBNEWBIE:
  |YKOPlayers are considered newbies until their 6th level, though
  most guilds will allow membership at level 5.

|MKB5:
  |YKOPlayers at level 5 gain the |YKB'whotitle' |YKOcommand.

|MKBCHAMPION:
  |YKOPlayers who reach level 50 show CHMP on the who list, gain
  the |YKB'ltitle' |YKOcommand, earn a free multichar slot, and can
  join a compatible second guild.

|MKBRENOWN:
  |YKOPlayers who reach level 100 receive a renown label on who:
  HERO, ADV, or VILN.

|MKBLEGEND:
  |YKOPlayers who reach level 150.
  LEGEND+ players gain the ability to register a free mythic
  character, and earn a second free multichar slot.

|MKBEPIC:
  |YKOPlayers who reach level 200 show EPIC on the who list.

|MKBMYTHIC:
  |YKOPlayers who reach level 250 stand at the mortal peak. Mythic
  characters may optionally |YKBremort|YKO: return to level 1, keep
  their wealth and belongings, and earn a permanent boon point
  for every rebirth. See |YKBhelp remort|YKO and |YKBhelp boons|YKO.
